---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Tools — May">
  <section class="page-header">
    <h1>Clarity tools</h1>
    <p class="page-sub">
      Guided experiences to examine what you're thinking, feeling, and deciding.
      Each tool is based on a real thinking framework — and adapted for the way
      life actually happens.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="tools-content">

    <!-- Decide -->
    <div class="tool-category" id="decidir">
      <h2>Decide</h2>
      <p class="category-sub">For when you have too many options and not enough clarity.</p>

      <div class="tools-grid">
        <a href="/ferramentas/medo-na-mesa" class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-number">01</div>
          <h3>Fear Setting</h3>
          <p>Name what you're avoiding. Separate real fear from inflated fear. Discover the cost of not acting.</p>
          <span class="tool-origin">Based on Fear Setting — Tim Ferriss</span>
          <span class="tool-time">~15 min</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/ferramentas/tres-futuros" class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-number">02</div>
          <h3>3 Plausible Futures</h3>
          <p>Imagine three honest versions of your next chapter. Not to choose in your head — to feel which one calls for a test.</p>
          <span class="tool-origin">Based on Odyssey Plan — Design Your Life</span>
          <span class="tool-time">~20 min</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/ferramentas/sim-inteiro" class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-number">03</div>
          <h3>Hell Yes or No</h3>
          <p>Separate a true yes from an "I think I should." To stop saying yes out of obligation.</p>
          <span class="tool-origin">Based on Hell Yes or No — Derek Sivers</span>
          <span class="tool-time">~10 min</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Listen to yourself -->
    <div class="tool-category" id="se-ouvir">
      <h2>Listen to yourself</h2>
      <p class="category-sub">For when you feel something but can't name it.</p>

      <div class="tools-grid">
        <a href="/ferramentas/bussola-interna" class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-number">04</div>
          <h3>Inner Compass</h3>
          <p>Use your body as a guide. Discover if what you feel is healthy fear or real misalignment.</p>
          <span class="tool-origin">Based on Martha Beck — Finding Your Own North Star</span>
          <span class="tool-time">~12 min</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/ferramentas/auditoria-de-energia" class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-number">05</div>
          <h3>Energy Audit</h3>
          <p>Map what drains you and what restores you. To reorganize life around what truly matters.</p>
          <span class="tool-origin">May curation</span>
          <span class="tool-time">~15 min</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Communicate -->
    <div class="tool-category" id="comunicar">
      <h2>Communicate</h2>
      <p class="category-sub">For when you need to say something hard without attacking or shutting down.</p>

      <div class="tools-grid">
        <a href="/ferramentas/o-que-quero-dizer" class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-number">06</div>
          <h3>What I Really Want to Say</h3>
          <p>Translate judgment, anger, and confusion into something clear and honest. For conversations you've been putting off.</p>
          <span class="tool-origin">Based on Nonviolent Communication — Marshall Rosenberg</span>
          <span class="tool-time">~15 min</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/ferramentas/prototipos-de-futuro" class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-number">07</div>
          <h3>Future Prototypes</h3>
          <p>Instead of deciding everything in your head, design 3 small tests. To experience a life before quitting everything.</p>
          <span class="tool-origin">Based on Design Your Life</span>
          <span class="tool-time">~15 min</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .page-header {
    max-width: 680px;
    margin: 5rem auto 4rem;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .page-header h1 { font-size: 2.4rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

  .page-sub {
    font-size: 1rem !important;
    line-height: 1.7 !important;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  .tools-content {
    max-width: 960px;
    margin: 0 auto 6rem;
    padding: 0 2rem;
  }

  .tool-category {
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
    padding-top: 1rem;
  }

  .tool-category h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .category-sub {
    font-size: 0.9rem !important;
    color: var(--ink-muted) !important;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .tools-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .tool-card {
    background: white;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 2rem;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    display: block;
    position: relative;
  }

  .tool-card:hover {
    border-color: #c8c8c0;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
  }

  .tool-number {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .tool-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
  }

  .tool-card p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .tool-origin {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }

  .tool-time {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
</style>
